I’ve been having an extra hard time recently because none of my friends are really talking to me. My brain knows it’s because they’re in college, busy with their own stuff, but my anxiety still tells me otherwise. I feel like people look down on me when I get like this

Honestly, the only reason I’m semi open to sharing this on twitter is because I feel less seen, less exposed. I’m still putting how I feel out there, but most likely little to no people see it, and that makes me feel a little better
